type: web_research
title: 暗号通貨情報収集システム & Dual Investment自動化トレードシステム 総合リサーチ
created: "2026-02-08T15:34:39.194Z"
updated: "2026-02-08T15:39:13.959Z"
key_insights[22]: "Lambda/Kappa architecture pattern: Kafka + Flink/Spark + ClickHouse/Druid for real-time crypto data pipeline",CCXT supports 100+ exchanges in JS/TS/Python/C#/PHP/Go - unified API for multi-exchange connectivity,"Bitget API V2 Earn endpoints: Savings (flexible/fixed), Shark Fin, but Dual Investment API not explicitly documented in public results","Key OSS trading bots: Freqtrade, Passivbot (Bitget supported), Hummingbot, Superalgos, OpenTrader","Sentiment analysis APIs: LunarCrush, Santiment, BittsAnalytics, StockGeist, Augmento, Zenpulsar","Whale tracking: Whale Alert, Nansen (300M+ labeled addresses), Arkham Intelligence, CryptoMeter","On-chain analytics pricing: Glassnode Advanced $29/mo, CryptoQuant Advanced $29/mo, Professional tiers $799/mo","DefiLlama: fully open-source, 200+ blockchains, 2000+ DeFi protocols, free API","Dune Analytics: custom SQL queries on 100+ blockchains, community dashboards","Risk management: 1% rule position sizing, Kelly Criterion, ATR-based stop loss, tiered exits, VaR monitoring",Kafka+ClickHouse pipeline handles 230K blockchain events/sec with sub-500ms latency,"CoinGecko: 24M+ tokens, 1700+ exchanges (best for breadth); CoinAPI: 380+ exchanges with tick-level data (best for depth)",Dual Investment の本質はオプションのプレミアム売り（Covered Call / Cash-Secured Put）,Buy Low = Cash-Secured Put（プット売り）、Sell High = Covered Call（コール売り）,Wheel Strategy（ホイール戦略）= Buy Low → Sell High のサイクル回転,APRが高い = ターゲットが近い = 転換確率が高い = リスクが高い,"Auto-Compound/Auto-Renewal で複利効果を最大化可能（Binance, OKX）",元本保証なし（Non-principal protected）が全取引所共通,取引所は利益相反の立場（条件設定者かつカウンターパーティ）,DeFi Option Vault（Ribbon Finance等）で取引所リスク分散可能,短期（1-5日）回転が初心者に推奨、OTM 5-15%のストライク設定,Bybit最大500% APR表示、Bitget最大302%、実効利回りは大幅に低い
refs[15]: "CCXT: github.com/ccxt/ccxt - 100+ exchanges unified API","Freqtrade: github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade - OSS trading bot","Passivbot: github.com/enarjord/passivbot - supports Bitget","OpenTrader: github.com/Open-Trader/opentrader - DCA & Grid strategies","Bitget API V2 Earn: bitget.com/api-doc/earn/sharkfin/Shark-Products","Bitget API Docs: bitget.com/api-doc/common/intro","DefiLlama: defillama.com - open source DeFi analytics","Dune Analytics: dune.com - SQL-based blockchain analytics","LunarCrush: lunarcrush.com - social sentiment API","Santiment: santiment.net - on-chain + social analytics","Whale Alert: whale-alert.io - blockchain transaction tracker","Hummingbot: hummingbot.org - open source market making","Superalgos: superalgos.org - open source trading platform","tiagosiebler/bitget-api: Node.js Bitget API wrapper","レポート: /Users/matsumototoshihiko/Desktop/開発2026/暗号通貨システム/dual_investment_research_report.md"
recommendations[16]: Use Kafka + ClickHouse as core data pipeline for real-time analytics,"CCXT for multi-exchange connectivity, Bitget SDK for exchange-specific features",LunarCrush API + Santiment for sentiment data layer,Freqtrade or Passivbot as base for trading bot (both support Bitget),DefiLlama free API for DeFi TVL tracking,"CoinGecko API for broad market data, CoinAPI for institutional-grade depth",Grafana + InfluxDB/Prometheus for monitoring dashboard,Telegram Bot API for real-time notifications,Redis for caching and message queuing,"PostgreSQL for persistent state, Redis for hot data",初心者はBTC/ETH + 短期1-3日 + OTM10%以上から開始,ホイール戦略（Buy Low ↔ Sell High サイクル）が最も体系的,全資金の30-50%をDIに配分、残りは流動性確保,複数取引所に分散（1取引所40%上限）,Auto-Compoundは週次で監視、トレンド転換時に手動停止,テクニカル分析のサポート/レジスタンスにターゲット設定
findings[7]: "Bitget, Binance, OKX, Bybit, Crypto.com, KuCoin, Nexo, Gate.io が主要プラットフォーム",OKXのみETH/BTC暗号通貨間Dual Investmentに対応,"Bybitは1,3,5日の超短期特化、21通貨ペア",Binanceが教育コンテンツ最充実、Top 6戦略ガイドあり,中国語圏の知乎では双币投資の具体的な戦略記事は見つからず,日本語圏ではデュアルインベストメントの情報が極めて少ない,IV（インプライド・ボラティリティ）分析でエントリータイミング最適化可能
